OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FA man who murdered and dismembered a
OL,7,Flodger before leaving packages of body
OL,8,Fparts along the Bournemouth seafront
OL,9,Fhas had his minimum prison term
OL,10,Fincreased at the Court of Appeal.
OL,12,FBenjamin Atkins, 49, was convicted of
OL,13,Fthe murder of 49-year-old Simon
OL,14,FShotton, whose legs were found by a
OL,15,Fmember of the public in the Boscombe
OL,16,Farea of the Dorset seaside resort in
OL,17,FAugust 2023.
