OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FMr Shotton had been living in a tent
OL,7,Fin the garden of the flat Atkins
OL,8,Fshared with his girlfriend, 39-year-
OL,9,Fold Debbie Pereira, in Aylesbury Road,
OL,10,FBoscombe, giving the defendants drugs
OL,11,Fin lieu of paying rent.
OL,13,FIn July, a judge at Winchester Crown
OL,14,FCourt jailed Atkins for a minimum of
OL,15,F19 years and handed a four-year
OL,16,Fsentence to Pereira after she was
OL,17,Facquitted of murder but convicted of
OL,18,Fperverting the course of justice.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
