OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FHowever, following a reference from
OL,7,Fthe Solicitor General under the unduly
OL,8,Flenient sentencing scheme, both
OL,9,Fsentences were increased at a hearing
OL,10,Fon Tuesday.
OL,12,FAtkins will now face a minimum term of
OL,13,F21 years, while Pereira's sentence for
OL,14,Fperverting the course of justice was
OL,15,Fincreased to six years.
OL,17,FLouise Oakley, for the Solicitor
OL,18,FGeneral, told the Court of Appeal that
OL,19,Fa fight broke out between Mr Shotton
OL,20,Fand Atkins on August 18 2023.
