OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FDuring his trial, Atkins admitted to
OL,7,Fkilling Mr Shotton at the couple's
OL,8,Fhome and dismembering his body but
OL,9,Fclaimed he had acted out of self-
OL,10,Fdefence.
OL,12,FHowever, Ms Oakley said: "The learned
OL,13,F(sentencing) judge concluded that the
OL,14,Fviolence inflicted on Simon Shotton
OL,15,Fwas ferocious and unnecessary."
