OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FThe barrister told the court that
OL,7,FAtkins "systematically" dismembered Mr
OL,8,FShotton's body "over a number of
OL,9,Fdays", and later tried to burn the
OL,10,Flodger's head in a back garden fire
OL,11,Fpit.
OL,13,FShe said: "Only tiny fragments were
OL,14,Fever recovered. Atkins has never said
OL,15,Fwhat he did with the rest of his head."
OL,17,FMr Shotton's torso was discovered in a
OL,18,Fsuitcase in Boscombe Chine Gardens on
OL,19,FSeptember 6.
