OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FMs Oakley told the court that the
OL,7,Fmurder was aggravated by elements
OL,8,Fincluding Mr Shotton's dismemberment
OL,9,Fand how his belongings were sold after
OL,10,Fhis death.
OL,12,FShe continued: "Bearing in mind all of
OL,13,Fthose matters, the increase of four
OL,14,Fyears of the minimum term of 15 years
OL,15,Fwas too little."
OL,17,FJudges at the Court of Appeal were
OL,18,Ftold there was an "extensive cleaning
OL,19,Foperation to remove all traces of
OL,20,Fblood from the property" by Atkins and
OL,21,FPereira.
