OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FPereira did not take part in the
OL,7,Ffight, but did not call the emergency
OL,8,Fservices, and acted as a "decoy" when
OL,9,FAtkins stole a hacksaw, the court was
OL,10,Ftold.
OL,12,FMs Oakley said: "Over a two week
OL,13,Fperiod, Miss Pereira participated in
OL,14,Fthe process... She allowed her
OL,15,Fproperty to be used and took active
OL,16,Fsteps to help him."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUpD@`O]tD@QOUxD@SO]
