OL,3,CMan who murdered and dismembered
OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FZafar Ali KC, for Atkins, said his
OL,7,Fsentence was not unduly lenient and
OL,8,Fthat the sentencing judge "was best
OL,9,Fplaced to fully understand the nuances
OL,10,Fof the case".
OL,12,FHe added that the judge, Mrs Justice
OL,13,FStacey, was an experienced High Court
OL,14,Fjudge who was "at all times proactive"
OL,15,Fduring the six-week trial.
OL,17,FIgnatius Hughes KC, for Pereira, said
OL,18,Fthat she had a "so much secondary"
OL,19,Frole.
