OL,4,Clodger has sentence increased
OL,6,FLord Justice Bean, sitting with Mr
OL,7,FJustice Johnson and Mrs Justice
OL,8,FHeather Williams, continued: "Even if
OL,9,FAtkins' criminality had been limited
OL,10,Fto the killing itself and the
OL,11,Fsubsequent acts had not taken place,
OL,12,Fthe case would have required a minimum
OL,13,Fterm well in excess of 15 years.
OL,15,F"But of course, Atkins' criminality
OL,16,Fwas not so limited."
